# Project Initialization Plan

## Step 1

Verify Development Environment

Commands:

```bash
node -v
npm -v
git --version
```

Objective:

Confirm all required tools are installed.

---

## Step 2

Create React Project

Command:

```bash
npm create vite@latest
```

Objective:

Generate the React project structure.

---

## Step 3

Install Dependencies

Command:

```bash
npm install
```

Objective:

Install project packages.

---

## Step 4

Configure Tailwind CSS

Objective:

Prepare styling system.

---

## Step 5

Create Folder Structure

Objective:

Organize project architecture.

---

## Step 6

Start Development Server

Command:

```bash
npm run dev
```

Objective:

Launch local development environment.

