# Git Workflow Strategy

## Daily Workflow

### Check Status

```bash
git status
```

Purpose:

Review project changes.

---

### Stage Specific Files

```bash
git add filename
```

Purpose:

Track only relevant changes.

---

### Commit Changes

```bash
git commit -m "meaningful message"
```

Purpose:

Create project checkpoints.

---

### Push Changes

```bash
git push
```

Purpose:

Upload commits to GitHub.

